industrious /ɪnˈdʌstrɪəs/

1. ADJ If you describe someone as industrious , you mean they work very hard. 勤奋的 [ADV with v] 

例： She was an industrious and willing worker. 她是个勤劳肯干的工人。 

2. industriously ADV 

例： Peggy paints industriously all through the summer. 佩吉整个夏天都在勤奋作画。

</div>

